```
**TRANSFORM my current web app → Gen Z 2026 playful immersive design for 20-year-olds**

Current site structure: https://ratha.mindset-it.online/ (header/nav/hero/cards/buttons/sections)

**KEEP ALL functionality, HTML structure, content, and links exactly the same**
**ONLY REPLACE visual design/CSS** with these Gen Z trends they love:

## 🎨 COMPLETE NEW VISUAL SYSTEM
```
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=Pacifico&display=swap');

:root {
  --neon-pink: #ff00ff; --neon-green: #00ff88; --neon-blue: #00d4ff; --neon-yellow: #ffaa00;
  --dark-bg: #0f0f23; --main-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0033 0%, #2d1b69 50%, #ff6b9d 100%);
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body { 
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; 
  background: var(--main-gradient); 
  color: #fff; 
  line-height: 1.7;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

header { 
  background: rgba(15,15,35,0.95); 
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px); 
  position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(255,0,255,0.3);
}
nav a { 
  color: #fff; padding: 12px 24px; 
  position: relative; text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
nav a:hover { color: var(--neon-pink); text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--neon-pink); }
nav a:hover::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 50%;
  width: 0; height: 3px; background: var(--neon-pink);
  animation: nav-expand 0.3s forwards;
}

.hero {
  min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  text-align: center; position: relative;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, var(--neon-green), transparent 50%), var(--main-gradient);
  perspective: 1000px;
}
.hero h1 {
  font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 20px;
  transform: rotateX(15deg) translateZ(50px);
  text-shadow: 0 0 40px var(--neon-blue);
  animation: hero-float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.hero p { font-size: 1.3rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 30px; opacity: 0.9; }
```

## 🃏 CARDS → 3D FLOATING BENTO BOXES
```
.container { max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
.cards-grid, .section { 
  display: grid; 
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
  gap: 28px; 
}
.card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); 
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,0,255,0.2); 
  border-radius: 28px;
  padding: 36px; 
  transform: translateY(20px) rotateX(8deg);
  transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.68,-0.55,0.265,1.55);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.card::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: -100%; width: 100%; height: 100%;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), transparent);
  transition: left 0.6s;
}
.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-25px) rotateX(0deg) scale(1.03);
  box-shadow: 0 35px 90px rgba(255,0,255,0.5);
  border-color: var(--neon-pink);
}
.card:hover::before { left: 100%; }
```

## ✨ BUTTONS → GOOEY NEON GLOW
```
.btn {
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--neon-pink), var(--neon-green));
  border: none; padding: 18px 36px; border-radius: 50px;
  font-family: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: #fff; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(255,0,255,0.4);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;
}
.btn:hover {
  transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.05);
  box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0,255,136,0.6);
}
```

## 🎭 ANIMATIONS (Essential)
```
@keyframes hero-float {
  0%,100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotateX(15deg); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotateX(10deg); }
}
@keyframes nav-expand { to { width: 100%; left: 0; } }
@keyframes card-pop {
  0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(50px) scale(0.9); }
  100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(20px) rotateX(8deg); }
}
.card { animation: card-pop 0.6s ease forwards; }
.card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
.card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
```

## 📱 MOBILE PERFECTION
```
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero { min-height: 80vh; padding: 20px; }
  .cards-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 20px; }
  .card { padding: 24px; transform: translateY(10px) rotateX(5deg); }
  nav a { padding: 10px 16px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
}
```

## 🎯 FINAL INSTRUCTION
**Generate COMPLETE updated HTML/CSS code** that:
1. Preserves ALL my current site's HTML structure/content/links
2. Applies ONLY these new CSS styles above
3. Makes it mobile-first, 60fps smooth
4. Feels like TikTok + cyberpunk bookstore = Gen Z addiction

**Make 20-year-olds unable to stop scrolling!**
```

